name: CNN
text:
Commentator @ananavarro reacts to the public backlash following Goya Foods CEO Robert Unanue's praise of Trump.

"Goya might be the biggest fish in the pond, but it is not the only fish in the pond... we are all free to do with our frijoles as we wish." https://t.co/8GmqVCtiUw https://t.co/KrKAALIS5I

Singer and songwriter Anita White, who performs as Lady A, calls the name change of the country trio formerly known as Lady Antebellum a “PR stunt.” https://t.co/OLKw86ZAvY https://t.co/jWVudW9O3j
